data.description: Comfortable studio in the heart of downtown Miami. Steps away from the metro mover/metro station and local retail business. West facing view of the Miami skyline. Amenities include, but are not limited to, state of the art pool, gym, pilates room, spinning room, spa, sauna, steam room, business center, and game room. Well priced unit and will move fast. The purchase price of the unit includes the Murphy bed shown in pictures.
